USER STORIES
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Display welcome message.
2. Display menu and prompt user choice.
3. Display rules when appropriate option is chosen.
4. Exit Application when appropriate option is chosen.
5. Start game when appropriate option is chosen.
6. User prompted for the number of players.
7. Player order is randomly chosen and shown.
8. Dealer is chosen randomly and shown.
9. Each player is dealt 8 random cards.
10. User is shown their cards.
11. Player to the left of the dealer has turn.
12. During AI turn, the card played is shown.
13. During Human turn, the hand is shown, user is prompted to pick a card to play.
